column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Monday March 4 at 4:00 p.m.

column3: Traffic Advisory for New Circle Rd:
column4: Starting at 10 a.m., New Circle Rd between Nicholasville Rd and Harrodsburg Rd is scheduled to be shutdown two times in 10-15 minute intervals for overhead electrical work.

column3: Traffic Advisory for New Circle Rd:
column4: Inner loop traffic will be diverted to Nicholasville Rd.  Outer loop traffic will be diverted to Harrodsburg Rd.
